PrecisAppointment of MICHAEL BELL as Ambassador of Canada to the State of Israel; WILLIAM CLARKE as High Commmissioner for Canada in Malaysia; TERENE COLFER as Ambassador of Canada to the Islamic Republic of Iran; ALLAN CULHAM as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Guatemila, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of El Salvador; JACQUES CRÊTE as High Commissioner for Canada in the Co-operative Republic of Guyana; JEAN-MARC DUVAL as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Turkey, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Azerbaijan, the Republic of Georgia and the Republic of Turkmenistan; LUCIE EDWARDS as High Commissioner of Canada in the Republic of Sout Africa; SAMUEL HANSON as Ambassador of Canada to Bosnia and Herzegovina; RODNEY IRWIN as Ambassador of Canada to the Russian Fedeation, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Armecia; PHILIPPE KIRSCH as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Sweden; CÉCILE LATOUR as Ambassador of Canada to the Socialist Republic of Vietnam; NORMAND MAILHOT as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Cambodia; DONALD McLENNAN as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Poland, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Belarus; MARTA MOSZCZENSKA as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Hungary, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Slovenia; BRUNO PICARD as Ambassador of Canada to the Dominican Republic; DAVID PRESTON as High Commissioner for Canada in the People's Republic of Bangladesh; NEIL REEDER as High Commissioner for Canada in Brunel Darussalam; JACQUES SIMARD as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Tunisia, with concurrent accreditation to the Social People's Libyan Arab Jamahiriya; GERALD SKINNER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Kazakhstan, with concurrent accreditation to the Kyrgyz Republic and the Republic of Tajikistan; CHRISTOPHER THOMSON as Ambassador of Canada to the United Arab Emirates; and JAMES WALL as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Zimbabwe, with concurent accreditation to the Republic of Botswana, and as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Angola.
